{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Immerse wooden skewer sticks in cold water for 30 minutes. Cut turkey in thin strips of 2 x 10 cm and of 5 mm thickness. Skewer each strip of turkey onto skewer stick passing through the meat several times so that it is flat along the stick. Place all skewers in airtight container and set aside.","Place garlic cloves into mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>.","Add cayenne peppers, peanuts, peppercorns, yeast extract, orange peel, orange juice, sherry, brown sugar, paprika, vinegar and soy sauce and chop <b>10 sec\/speed 7<b>. Pour mixture over kebabs. Leave to marinate in refrigerator for at least 30 minutes.","Strain kebabs reserving the marinade. Pour the reserved marinade into mixing bowl and place Varoma dish into position. Place skewers inside, some perpendicular to others. Cover Varoma and steam <b>15 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Set Varoma aside and place skewers on a hot dish. Pour sauce over skewers and serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["500 g turkey meat, boneless, skinless","4 garlic cloves","2 fresh red chillies","30 g roasted salted peanuts","6 black peppercorns","1 tsp yeast extract (e.g. Bovril®, Cenovis®, Marmite®)","4 pieces orange zest, no white part (1,5 x 5 cm)","50 g orange juice, freshly squeezed","20 g dry sherry wine","30 g brown sugar","½ tsp ground paprika","1 tbsp vinegar","50 g soy sauce"]}],"id":"r127219","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-c6lIY_l4awc\/XZQHr7pO25I\/AAAAAAAAcK8\/rZXBolYJDDoauFGZwv6nWR28VaTI6aNaQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_p-F89Rx5EhP1LcIX.png","title":"Spicy turkey kebabs","publishedAt":"2017-08-07T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"19.2 g","fat":"5 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"7.45 g","calories":"637 kJ \/ 152 kcal"},"usefulItems":"air-tight container, wood skewers, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Note to translator: Add brand of yeast extract to ingredient list that is available in your country. &gt;&gt;delete after reading","Check that the sauce is well reduced. If not, cook again <b>2-3 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b> without the measuring cup."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h","6 portions"]}